                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card bg-light border-0 h-100">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h6 class="text-primary">üîß Correct Your Data</h6>
                                    <p class="small mb-0">Notice we spelled your name wrong? Think your profile makes you look like a serial ceramic frog collector? Let us know!</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row mt-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
