                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="card bg-light border-0 h-100">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h6 class="text-primary">üì¶ Download Your Data</h6>
                                    <p class="small mb-0">Want a copy of everything? We'll package it up nicely for you. Think of it as a digital scrapbook of your selling adventures.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3 mt-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-baby me-2"></i>Kids and Privacy
                    </h3>
                    <p>This site is designed for adults. If you're under 13, please ask your parents before using this site. If you're 13-17, make sure your parents are cool with you selling that Pokemon card collection.</p>

                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3 mt-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-2"></i>Changes to This Policy
                    </h3>
                    <p>Sometimes we might need to update this policy (hopefully to make it even funnier). When we do, we'll:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Post the new version here</li>
                        <li>Update the "last modified" date</li>
                        <li>Let you know if there are any major changes</li>
                        <li>Try to make the new version at least as entertaining as this one</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-primary mb-3 mt-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-question-circle me-2"></i>Questions? Concerns? Complaints About Our Ceramic Frog Jokes?
                    </h3>
